It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You won't need any equipmentThe workout has a The Adrenaline Rush and The Firestarter vibe.
The The Adrenaline Rush vibe means Heart-racing, full-body intensity, unpredictable challenges. This is especially good for Those who crave challenge, variety, and adrenaline. The The Firestarter vibe means Fast, explosive, and electrifying. Short but devastating. This is especially good for When you only have 10-20 minutes but want to give 1000%..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.
